# thoth_policy_exception

Creates and reads a policy exception request.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "thoth_policy_exception" "crm_export" {
  violation_id           = "vio-7f8c"
  agent_id               = "crm-agent"
  tool_name              = "export_records"
  requested_by           = "udev123"
  business_justification = "Month-end reconciliation export for finance close"
  frequency_estimate     = "weekly"
  data_sensitivity       = "financial"
  alternatives_considered = "Manual CSV export is too slow and error-prone"
}
```
